## 🏃‍♂️ **STEP-BY-STEP LAUNCH PROCESS**

### **STEP 1: Choose & Register Domain** (5 minutes)

#### Option A: Namecheap (Recommended)
1. Go to https://namecheap.com
2. Search for: `toxexpress.com`
3. Add to cart ($8.98/year)
4. Create account
5. Complete payment
6. **Domain is yours!**

#### Option B: Hostinger (Domain + Hosting Bundle)
1. Go to https://hostinger.com
2. Choose "Web Hosting" plan ($2.99/month)
3. Search domain: `toxexpress.com`
4. Add free domain with hosting
5. Complete setup

### **STEP 2: Setup Hosting Account** (10 minutes)

#### For Namecheap Hosting:
1. Login to Namecheap account
2. Go to "Hosting" → "Add Hosting"
3. Choose "Stellar Plus" plan ($2.88/month)
4. Select your domain
5. Complete payment
6. **Hosting activated!**

#### For Hostinger:
1. Login to Hostinger account
2. Hosting account auto-created with domain purchase
3. Access control panel

### **STEP 3: Upload Website Files** (15 minutes)

#### Method 1: File Manager (Easiest)
1. Login to hosting control panel (cPanel/Plesk)
2. Find "File Manager"
3. Navigate to `public_html` folder
4. Upload all files from your `TRANSPORT WORLD` folder:
   ```
   • index.html
   • admin.html
   • dashboard.html
   • server.js
   • package.json
   • sitemap.xml
   • robots.txt
   • css/ folder
   • js/ folder
   • data/ folder (if exists)
   ```

#### Method 2: FTP Upload
1. Download FileZilla (free): https://filezilla-project.org
2. Get FTP credentials from hosting welcome email
3. Connect to server
4. Upload entire `TRANSPORT WORLD` folder to `public_html`

### **STEP 4: Setup Node.js Backend** (10 minutes)

#### For cPanel Hosting:
1. Login to cPanel
2. Find "Node.js" or "Application Manager"
3. Create new application:
   ```
   Application URL: /
   Application root: public_html
   Application startup file: server.js
   ```
4. Click "Create"
5. Application will auto-start

#### For VPS/Cloud Hosting:
1. SSH into server
2. Navigate to website folder
3. Install dependencies:
   ```bash
   npm install
   ```
4. Start server:
   ```bash
   npm start
   ```
5. Setup PM2 for production:
   ```bash
   npm install -g pm2
   pm2 start server.js
   pm2 startup
   pm2 save
   ```

### **STEP 5: Configure SSL Certificate** (5 minutes)

1. Login to hosting control panel
2. Find "SSL/TLS" or "Security"
3. Choose "Let's Encrypt"
4. Select your domain
5. Click "Install"
6. **HTTPS enabled automatically**

### **STEP 6: DNS Configuration** (5 minutes)

#### If domain and hosting are separate:
1. Login to domain registrar (Namecheap)
2. Go to "Domain List" → "Manage"
3. Click "Advanced DNS"
4. Add these records:
   ```
   Type: A
   Host: @
   Value: YOUR_HOSTING_IP (from hosting welcome email)
   TTL: Automatic
   ```
5. Save changes
6. **Wait 24-48 hours for DNS propagation**

### **STEP 7: Test Everything** (10 minutes)

#### Test Website:
1. Visit: `https://toxexpress.com`
2. Check all pages load
3. Test contact form
4. Test shipment tracking

#### Test Admin Dashboard:
1. Visit: `https://toxexpress.com/admin.html`
2. Login with: `ToxExpress2024Admin`
3. Test shipment management
4. Check visitor analytics

#### Test Mobile:
1. Open site on phone
2. Test all features
3. Check responsiveness

### **STEP 8: Setup Google Visibility** (10 minutes)

#### Google Analytics:
1. Go to https://analytics.google.com
2. Create account → Property → Web
3. Enter: `https://toxexpress.com`
4. Get tracking code
5. Add to `<head>` of `index.html`

#### Google Search Console:
1. Go to https://search.google.com/search-console
2. Add property: `https://toxexpress.com`
3. Verify ownership (HTML file method)
4. Submit sitemap: `https://toxexpress.com/sitemap.xml`

### **STEP 9: Final Security Setup** (5 minutes)

#### Change Admin Password:
1. Login to admin dashboard
2. Go to Settings
3. Change password from default
4. Save new secure password

#### Setup Backups:
1. In hosting panel → "Backups"
2. Enable automatic daily backups
3. Test backup restoration

